Package: rchk0
Title: Raw Data Issue Tracker for Clinical Datasets
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Shushun", "Ren", email = "shushunr@umich.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for checking raw clinical datasets, identifying issues,
    and generating formatted Excel reports. Includes automated checks for
    visit discrepancies, early discontinuation dates, visit gaps, and more.
